 Career History



Professional

                                    Current                


Hudson Bay Capital Management LP


                  Hudson Bay Capital Management LP is a manager of alternative investment opportunities in the global markets targeting traditional and non-traditional sources of alpha by employing a diverse set of catalyst-driven absolute return strategies that are intended to be uncorrelated to each other and to the major indices. Our eight portfolio teams invest across the corporate capital structure and often trade around or in conjunction with an event or catalyst in an effort to exploit market inefficiencies.

Founded in December 2005, with Sander Gerber as Chief Investment Officer, the firm has 51 employees, including 26 investment/risk professionals, who seek to achieve persistently positive returns while maintaining a focus on risk management and capital preservation.                




Senior Vice President, Marketing

                                    Prior - 2015                


ICE Canyon LLC


                  ICE Canyon seeks to generate attractive risk-adjusted absolute returns and long-term value from specialist strategies in emerging markets (EM) and global credit investment strategies. The firm's strategies cover all sectors of the EM fixed income and global credit universe including: EM sovereign, EM local currency, EM corporate credit, EM bank loans, EM special situations, EM distressed, and other global credit opportunities. ICE Canyon’s investment philosophy aligns long-term value creation in global investing to the primary forces of global economic growth, corporate earnings, and new market opportunities. ICE Canton employs an integrated, bottom-up, research-driven, value-seeking investment approach using probabilistic scenario analysis as the basis for decision-making and asset allocation. Their investment approach is designed to identify and exploit asymmetrical market opportunities in which the risk of any permanent loss of capital is well contained and the investment strategy is positively linked to significant upside catalysts. ICE Canyon’s investment strategy targets core value, deep value, and event-driven investment opportunities.                




Head of Institutional Sales

                                    2010 - 2012                


Gotham Asset Management LLC


                  Gotham Asset Management, LLC is an equity management firm that offers domestic and international value investing strategies to institutional clients. Joel Greenblatt and Robert Goldstein serve as Managing Principals and co-CIOs for Gotham, with over 50 years of combined investment experience.

Gotham Asset Management uses a fundamental value discipline developed by Greenblatt, Goldstein and their team of investment professionals to manage both long only and long/short equity portfolios.                





 Other Affiliations




              Kerra Marmelstein is affiliated with
                            Hudson Bay Capital Management LP, ICE Canyon LLC, Gotham Asset Management LLC.
            





